{"title":"月儿圆（外一首）","authors":["梁上泉"],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":3,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"月儿圆（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梁上泉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弹起冬不拉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"琴声铮铮响不断，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"响不断，在召唤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唤来维族青年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏着两根弦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邀男约女聚湖畔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜庆节日跳得欢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人一旁打鼓点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踩着鼓点团团转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上圆月弄舞影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"圆月手鼓头上悬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓儿鸣，月儿伴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手鼓更比月儿圆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月儿双双照草滩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪与月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你爱昆仑雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我爱祁连月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二人相望更相亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两山相隔脉相接；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一在盆地南，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一在盆地北，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如我意绵绵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如你情切切。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你采油，我勘测，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送走多少昼和夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两山遥映雪与月；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月似雪样白，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪似月样洁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肝胆两相照，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤心紧相贴；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪有消，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月有缺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山岳长在情不绝！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}